pan> </p><ul style="text-indent: 0px; margin-left: 24px; list-style-position: outside; list-style-type: disc;"><li class="rvps7"> <span class="rvts7">Every action has a <span class="rvts7"><span class="rvts18">&quot;Settings&quot;</span> function.</span></span> </li></ul><p class="rvps7"><img alt="" style="vertical-align: middle; padding : 1px;" src="en/imgspec/Parametre_Action1.png"><span class="rvts7"> </span></p><p class="rvps7"><img alt="" style="vertical-align: middle; padding : 1px;" src="en/imgspec/Parametre_Action0.png"><span class="rvts7"> </span></p><p class="rvps7"> <span class="rvts7">By right clicking on this function you can edit the parameters of the action. A window opens in which you enter a comment to the action.</span> </p><p class="rvps7"> <span class="rvts7">On the <span class="rvts7"><span class="rvts18">&quot;Options&quot;</span></span></span> <span class="rvts7">of this window:</span> </p><ul style="text-indent: 0px; margin-left: 24px; list-style-position: outside; list-style-type: disc;"><ul style="text-indent: 0px; margin-left: 48px; list-style-position: outside; list-style-type: circle;"><li style="margin-left: 0px" class="rvps9"><img alt="" style="vertical-align: middle; padding : 1px;" src="en/imgspec/Parametre_Action3.png"> <span class="rvts7">if the box is checked the action will save the open document. Indeed we shall see later that certain</span> <a class="rvts17" href="Icnesdanslesconditionsetopration.html">terms</a> <span class="rvts7">and</span> <span class="rvts17">operations</span> <span class="rvts7">require opening or not the document.</span> </li><li style="margin-left: 0px" class="rvps9"><img alt="" style="vertical-align: middle; padding : 1px;" src="en/imgspec/Parametre_Action4.png"> <span class="rvts7">checked by default. In general the operation is applied in case of success (s) condition (s). If you uncheck this option, the operation will be applied in case of failure.</span> </li></ul></ul><p class="rvps7"> <span class=